dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contours and spot heights. "Surveyed 1954-55." Map show cantonment and municipal boundaries, street names, principal buildings, railways, and parks. Originally printed on 2 sheets, pasted together. "Reg. no. 591 MD'59 (I A.S. Party 6) -50000'60." "Reference list is printed on a separate sheet of paper". Our library does not have the companion reference sheet.
